name: iar
comment: Command-line utility for managing IAR (Inobulles ARchive) files
desc:
IAR (Inobulles ARchive) is a very lightweight and speedy archive file format which uses the `.iar` file extension.
This is a command-line utility which aids in packing and unpacking these IAR files.
Fuller documentation can be found in the IAR GitHub repository's `README.md` file.

WWW: https://github.com/inobulles/iar
